        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 7: immunogold EM showed Septin-3 (SEPT3) localized to mitochondria, double-membrane and multivesicular body-like structures and LC3B positive autophagic vesicles in cortical samples.\n\nFigure S3: immunogold EM showed Septin-3 (SEPT3) localized to the presynapse. No clear subcellular localization within the presynapse can be discerned from presented images.. Experimental description: supplemental figures; \"Fig. S3 Electron micrographs of mouse brain slice\"\n\nantibody:\nmouse anti-SEPT3, 1:50 (sc-74431, Santa Cruz)" ;
